```vba
Function CheckIfNumber(cell As Range) As String
    If IsNumeric(cell.Value) Then
        CheckIfNumber = "Number"
    Else
        CheckIfNumber = "Not a number"
    End If
End Function
```

You can use this function in your Excel sheet like any other function. For example, if you want to check if cell A1 contains a number, you can use:
